result.formatted_address: Wai Yue Building, New St, Sheung Wan, Hong Kong
result.name: Little Birdy

reviews.text:
I love the chicken wings here.
Even the burger is pretty good.
Staff speaks English pretty well so it’s very convenient for me since I’m no local.

Perfect place for a quick bite! 
Besides great chicken, they offer vegetarian options too, i got a halloumi burger today which was of decent quality and flavourful. 🤤
Price is a bit on the higher end as usual but it’s expected for anything in the area.
These guys know how to make a great sandwich. Had The OG and the Heisenberg - both excellent and packed with flavor.
Small shop off Poho. Tasty fried chicken served with a waffle, beer served too.
They know how to make chicken sexy.
